					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I've only skimmed this thread, but had an idea that might help with handling proportional font rendering. If this is being used on a handheld device, you could display everything rotated 90 degrees, so that you view the screen in a vertical orientation like a page. This would make each byte of tile data a vertical strip rather than horizontal, eliminating all the bit shifting when rendering a proportional font. Maybe this has already been discussed.</div>

