						<div class="postbody">A simple BASIC-style reader with a fixed-width font (i.e. 8x8 pixels per character) is easy. One with proportional fonts pushes the NES hardware since it requires so much bitmap storage. If I can figure something out, I'm going to try a quick implementation.</div>

